Package User

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Account
    the class User.Account extends the class User.Person
    it is used to create new account for a certain user
    Person
    the class User.Person is used to contain all the necessary informations about a certain person
    it is an abstract class, which all of its attributes and methods will inherited by the class User.Account
    UserList
    the class User.UserList is used to make a new list containing all the Accounts
    in this class we can manage (delete, add, modify) each User.Account individually
